{"type": "article", "id": 14957, "title": "沙发床", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-16T07:29:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 47, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606143617nbDypEHZNg30hCTu.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t沙发的设计常常与床联系起来，尽可能扩大座位面积以获得更多的功能。而这位俄罗斯设计师 Elena Sidorova 设计的沙发可以直接翻过来的铺成床，沙发的外面的软垫是羊毛，座位里面的空间里可以放置枕头和床垫，需要时拿出来铺上，就是一张很非常舒适的单人床了。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142325szI1VdXEymkcRHY0.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"735\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.91875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261423269s4NzOXQRnpLCAwW.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"324\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.405\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142327IsMCcGYi9Fk0Ef1y.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"489\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.61125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142328lwybgpJ0xSsqmv6a.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"343\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.42875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142329nCeLwZUXB5blSuGV.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"615\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.76875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}